name: event_date
description: Date of the session (parsed from GA4 event_date)

name: users
description: Number of distinct users with at least one session on the given date

name: sessions
description: Total number of sessions on the given date

name: engaged_sessions
description: Number of sessions with at least one user_engagement event

name: engaged_session_rate
description: Ratio of engaged sessions to total sessions

name: avg_engagement_time_sec_per_session
description: Average engagement time per session in seconds

name: total_conversions
description: Total number of conversion events on the given date

name: conversions_per_session
description: Average number of conversions per session
